Domain name: NMG.com
OUs Created: Finance, HR,IT,Operations
Security groups created: Finance-Users, HR-Users, IT-Users,Operations-Users
Purpose of each OU:
Finance: Contains user accounts, computers and assets belonging to the accounting and financial department to manage targeted access to payroll and budgeting resources.
HR: Isolates Human Resources personnel and assets to secure sensitive employee records and onboarding data.
IT: Houses the information technology team, administrative accounts, and technical assets responsible for network management and system security.
Operations: Contains users and systems managing daily business execution, production, or logistics workflows.
